        "original": "パパパパもっとずっとマイハンド",
        "english": "Pa-pa-pa-pa, more and more, my hand",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:22.000",
        "end": "03:24.000",
        "original": "キャットラビング\nLyrics, Music: 香椎モミ",
        "english": "Cat Loving\nLyrics, Music: Kashii Momi",
        "alignment_source": "visual_inference",
        "type": "on_screen_text"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:24.450",
        "end": "03:26.700",
        "original": "痛いことは嫌いですが",
        "english": "I hate painful things, but",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:26.700",
        "end": "03:30.200",
        "original": "君の手のひらは嫌いじゃない",
        "english": "I don't hate the palm of your hand",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:30.200",
        "end": "03:32.400",
        "original": "言葉は飴玉みたいに",
        "english": "Words are like candy",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:32.400",
        "end": "03:36.000",
        "original": "甘く広がってココロ満たす",
        "english": "Spreading sweetness and filling my heart",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:36.150",
        "end": "03:37.700",
        "original": "全然分かってない！",
        "english": "You don't understand at all!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:37.700",
        "end": "03:40.200",
        "original": "「永遠」言う通り 完全に不感症じゃない？",
        "english": "Just as \"eternity\" implies, aren't you completely insensitive?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:40.200",
        "end": "03:41.800",
        "original": "どこにいても？",
        "english": "No matter where I am?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:41.800",
        "end": "03:43.700",
        "original": "あ、なんで聞いてない？",
        "english": "Ah, why aren't you listening?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:43.700",
        "end": "03:47.600",
        "original": "元々あの子みたいに可愛くならなくちゃ",
        "english": "I've got to become cute like that girl from the start",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:47.750",
        "end": "03:49.700",
        "original": "愛は正味 そこはハメ",
        "english": "Love is essentially a trap",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:49.700",
        "end": "03:52.400",
        "original": "勿体無いのだって分からなくなる",
        "english": "I even lose track of what's a waste",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:52.550",
        "end": "03:54.600",
        "original": "曖昧また旅 趣味 ご褒美",
        "english": "Ambiguity, travels again, hobbies, rewards",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:54.600",
        "end": "03:57.600",
        "original": "もう安くなって遊ばれないように",
        "english": "So that I won't be cheapened and toyed with anymore",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:59.800",
        "end": "04:02.100",
        "original": "今日だって ちゃんと内緒の傷繕い",
        "english": "Even today, I'm properly mending my secret wounds",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:02.250",
        "end": "04:04.400",
        "original": "ニャン体 よじ込みするから",
        "english": "I'll curl my cat-like body in, so...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:04.400",
        "end": "04:05.800",
        "original": "愛して",
        "english": "Love me",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:06.000",
        "end": "04:08.100",
        "original": "Everybody today is a rubbing day.",
        "english": "Everybody today is a rubbing day.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:08.100",
        "end": "04:11.100",
        "original": "Get it, get it, this is my courtship.",
        "english": "Get it, get it, this is my courtship.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:11.250",
        "end": "04:13.300",
        "original": "Any, any, anytime's funny me.",
        "english": "Any, any, anytime's funny me.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:13.300",
        "end": "04:17.100",
        "original": "Give me, give me, love me, my darling.",
        "english": "Give me, give me, love me, my darling.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:17.250",
        "end": "04:20.100",
        "original": "アイタイ間違いなんて みんな言う",
        "english": "Everyone says \"I want to see you\" is a mistake",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:20.100",
        "end": "04:23.700",
        "original": "取り憑かれてるって",
        "english": "That I'm possessed",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:23.750",
        "end": "04:26.100",
        "original": "ならこの胸で美しく",
        "english": "Then, if it's within this breast, beautifully...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:26.100",
        "end": "04:29.600",
        "original": "締め付けるような切なさならば",
        "english": "...a tightening sort of sadness",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:29.650",
        "end": "04:31.400",
        "original": "選ぶ言葉と",
        "english": "The words I choose and",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:31.400",
        "end": "04:33.200",
        "original": "惑う指先",
        "english": "My wavering fingertips",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:33.200",
        "end": "04:35.300",
        "original": "崩せない横顔",
        "english": "That profile I can't break",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:35.300",
        "end": "04:36.700",
        "original": "私しか知らない",
        "english": "Only I know",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:36.750",
        "end": "04:38.200",
        "original": "あ、乱高下 ご機謙もしかして",
        "english": "Ah, violent fluctuations, your mood perhaps...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:38.200",
        "end": "04:41.000",
        "original": "今日は優しく撫でてくれるのかな？",
        "english": "Will you pet me gently today?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:41.150",
        "end": "04:43.700",
        "original": "君のそれが耐えられるの",
        "english": "The one who can withstand that part of you...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:43.700",
        "end": "04:47.100",
        "original": "障害で私だけなんだよね",
        "english": "Is only me in this whole life, right?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:47.250",
        "end": "04:49.100",
        "original": "あからさまに 体まさに",
        "english": "Obviously, my body is truly",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:49.100",
        "end": "04:52.400",
        "original": "もう病んで離れられないよね",
        "english": "Sick of it already, yet I can't leave, right?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:52.550",
        "end": "04:53.600",
        "original": "そうだよね",
        "english": "That's right, isn't it?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:53.600",
        "end": "04:55.300",
        "original": "感情は徐々に",
        "english": "Emotions, gradually",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:55.300",
        "end": "04:57.100",
        "original": "歌声は徐々に",
        "english": "Voices, gradually",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:57.100",
        "end": "05:00.000",
        "original": "蒙昧末路のように",
        "english": "Like a path of ignorance towards the end",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      }
    ],
    "model_name": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
  }
}